  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  import { Playground, PropsTable } from 'docz'
import Credits from './'

export default class MDXContent extends React.Component {
  constructor(props) {
    super(props)
    this.layout = null
  }
  render() {
    const { components, ...props } = this.props

    return <MDXTag
             name="wrapper"
             
             components={components}>
<MDXTag name="h1" components={components} props={{"id":"credits-component"}}>{`Credits component`}</MDXTag>
